{
  "_comment": "Pilot capture: Klaviyo pre-connection landing + post-Add-New-Connection state. The post-connection variant uses the real WPForms jconfirm modal (real plugin, not the snapshot's mirror) to add a connection, then plays around with the resulting form to exercise more fields.",
  "variants": [
